<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV25">
<l>varattiṉiṟci rattaimikka vāḷeyiṟṟu maṟṟava</l>
<l>ṉurattiṉiṟka rattaivaittu kirttalattai yūṉṟiṉā</l>
<l>yirattinīyi teṉṉapoyyi rantamaṇva yiṟṟuḷē</l>
<l>karattiyuṉka ruttaiyāvar kāṇavallar kaṇṇaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who placed [Your] hands on and drove in the nails into</l>
<l>the chest of the bright-toothed foe, who had ample faith in [his] boons!</l>
<l>You begged [for the earth]. What is this deception? You concealed</l>
<l>the earth that [You] begged for inside [Your] stomach!</l>
<l rend="indent">O Kṛṣṇa! Who can perceive Your intention?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
